                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 718.1915/215.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Panama</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-10-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 7, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Local politics and attitude of Costa Rican newspapers resulted in unanimous
                    adoption by National Assembly yesterday of resolution that the boundary dispute
                    should not be considered ended. Full rejection of award may be expected earlier
                    than indicated my telegram October 1.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Price</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
